actions.name: AssociateUser
actions.description: Grants permission to associate a subscribed user to an instance launched with license manager user subscriptions products

actions.name: DeregisterIdentityProvider
actions.description: Grants permission to deregister Microsoft Active Directory with license-manager-user-subscriptions for a product

actions.name: DisassociateUser
actions.description: Grants permission to disassociate a subscribed user from an instance launched with license manager user subscriptions products

actions.name: ListIdentityProviders
actions.description: Grants permission to list all the Identity Providers on license manager user subscriptions

actions.name: ListInstances
actions.description: Grants permission to list all the instances launched with license manager user subscription products

actions.name: ListProductSubscriptions
actions.description: Grants permission to lists all the product subscriptions for a product and identity provider

actions.name: ListUserAssociations
actions.description: Grants permission to list all the users associated to an instance launched for a product

actions.name: RegisterIdentityProvider
actions.description: Grants permission to registers Microsoft Active Directory with license-manager-user-subscriptions for a product

actions.name: StartProductSubscription
actions.description: Grants permission to start product subscription for a user on a registered active directory for a product

actions.name: StopProductSubscription
actions.description: Grants permission to stop product subscription for a user on a registered active directory for a product
